026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34088,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/04\/01\/believers-praise-even-in-death\/","url_meta":{"origin":34940,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Hamd: Believers praise Allah even as they die","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 1, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, the believer is in good shape in every situation. He praises Allah Almighty even while his soul is taken out of his body.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 2475 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Arna'ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0633\u064d \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32649,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/07\/05\/seven-sadaqah-al-jariyah\/","url_meta":{"origin":34940,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Charity: Seven types of ongoing charity after death","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 5, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cSeven deeds of a servant continue to be rewarded after his death while he is in his grave: knowledge to be learned, constructing a canal, digging a well, planting a date-palm tree, building a mosque,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0